{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/6.gif?t=1720570559\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build and protect cities with factories in an infinite hex world.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Best way to play the game: Singleplayer / Mouse and Keyboard.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Balance production and consumption of your city.<br></li><li> Research new technologies,<br></li><li> Build more factories, <br></li><li> Build more cities,<br></li><li> Explore new tiles and new planets,<br></li><li> Protect your cities from alien sabotage,<br></li><li> Use the Map Maker to build your own worlds, <br></li><li> Get Steam Achievements, <br></li><li> Compare with other players with the Steam Leaderboards!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer Online Stock Exchange.</h2>Reach tier 5 to be able to trade items in the Stock Market with other players online in real-time.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/5.gif?t=1720570559\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features in this prototype:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 41 Initial Buildings (Build Roads, Miners, Farms, Factories, Houses and Services)<br></li><li> 15 Initial types of Tiles<br></li><li> 7 Research areas<br></li><li> 2 Citizen class<br></li><li> 1 Alien Saboteur class<br></li><li> 1 Spaceship class<br></li><li> 39 Parts to produce<br></li><li> 2 Planets (Earth and Moon)<br></li><li> Terraforming<br></li><li> Testing phase of the Online Stock Market</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/4.gif?t=1720570559\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Some <strong>thoughts </strong>for the next versions of the game: </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> + new Buildings (More factories, farms, power generators, miners...)<br></li><li> + new tile types (Desert, uranium, pasture, bauxite, oil...)<br></li><li> + parts to produce ( Canned Food, Tools, Satellites, Smartphones...)<br></li><li> + Citizen Classes (Engineers, Scientists, Ecologists...)<br></li><li> + types of houses<br></li><li> + types of services (Health Center, School, Stadium...)<br></li><li> Manual Turrets, Automatic Turrets and Spaceship to fight new enemies</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/3.gif?t=1720570559\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">And more thoughts... </h2>Add a Character<br><br>Start adding content to the  wiki on \\fandom<br>Create all the story of the game<br>Make new planets and travelling<br>Add supply pods<br>Manual and Automatic turrets to defend your cities<br>Spaceships to defend your cities<br>Sandbox mode<br>New missions to produce/atack/dominate new places<br>More decorations<br>Mod support using Steam Workshop<br>Sell and buy items in-game (send them to other planets)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/2.gif?t=1720570559\" /><br><br><strong>This is a passion project that will go on for a long time.</strong><br><br>I'm a solo developer who also makes mods for Satisfactory and Factorio.<br><br>Aquila Industrial - Satisfactory Mods<br>DellAquila - Factorio Mods<br><br>Music by JuliusH from Pixabay<br>Italian translation by Micol Pennese<br>Portuguese translation by Andre Aquila<br>German translation by Astradaha<br>French translation by Thierry Lemieux-Raymond<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/1.gif?t=1720570559\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hexfactory First Medal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1958750/5842bef2490f22301f147ed7c22a50bfd04370ab.jpg"},{"name":"Iron Medal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1958750/a2c191890c05464afb5fe678494f3d31